question: Show network admin jobs and IT consultant jobs with a $70k salary.
sql_query1:
SELECT JobPostings.title 
FROM JobPostings
WHERE (JobPostings.itJobs = "Network Administrator" OR JobPostings.itJobs = "IT Consultant") AND JobPostings.salary = "$70,000"
sql_query2:
SELECT JobPostings.title 
FROM JobPostings
WHERE JobPostings.itJobs = "Network Administrator" OR JobPostings.itJobs = "IT Consultant" AND JobPostings.salary = "$70,000"
interpretation1: Show all jobs with a $70k salary for either the network admin or IT consultant role.
interpretation2: Show all the network admin job postings, also show the IT consultant jobs with a $70k salary.
